author: wn.com
title: Queensland Government urged to rethink Glencore as Aurukun bauxite mine preferred developer
text: A consortium seeking to mine rich bauxite deposits in Aurukun, in far north Queensland, is urging the State Government to reconsider its bid, amid growing uncertainty about Glencore's future. ...
